title: Adventure HQ - Khatib: An Indoor Adventure Center
blurb: Singapore's First Multi-Installation Indoor Adventure Centre
description: Adventure HQ is Singaporeâ€™s first multi-installation indoor adventure centre, spanning 2,800 square metres with a height of 20 metres. It features thrilling rock climbing walls, an urban climb zone, a challenging ropes course, a 165-metre-long indoor cave, and the first-of-its-kind 2-tiered, 7.5-metre high indoor free-fall slide in Singapore.
